{"tid":93871,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"盤 點 娛 圈 6 大 雞 隻！無 花 無 假 一 定 係 雞！","createTime":"2017-01-24T18:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T10:40:26.000Z","uid":53178,"like":121,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c767436a6f28e5b68dc55054dd8785be37674c9","tid":93871,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:11:00.000Z","msg":"大美人今次同大家點評娛樂雞隻！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鍾欣桐<br />\n生 肖 屬 雞 ！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n阿嬌天生黑色素較多，是一隻不折不扣的烏絲雞后，口感較鞋，只能用於煲老火湯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/015150_19a7de2d2cc17825f988818a95b55d04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F015150_19a7de2d2cc17825f988818a95b55d04.jpg&h=f28f407c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1000Ct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1000Ct.jpg&h=53a20553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/015151_a162628146fec83b5311baec48bee52c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F015151_a162628146fec83b5311baec48bee52c.jpg&h=c27b6543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>鄭希怡<br />\n生 肖 屬 雞 ！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n在歡樂滿東華中為700萬觀眾帶來不少歡樂的鄭列瓊，早年在加拿大登台露出驚世黑提，上剝下露後，估計和阿嬌一樣，同屬烏絲雞品種。<br />\n<br />\n露黑提無碼YouTube link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W3Pj35RvcD8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW3Pj35RvcD8&d=D%2BlS2%2BkA0YQiF9CPsTU8cJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8f9f702d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W3Pj35RvcD8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvH3RT4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvH3RT4.jpg&h=7c9b2b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/015425_2f82c1a7e8dd19eb776a9afd436b7ae1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F015425_2f82c1a7e8dd19eb776a9afd436b7ae1.jpg&h=a2ba55f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/015425_4e88f397ca5b459d6ee4f1536eddb73d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F015425_4e88f397ca5b459d6ee4f1536eddb73d.jpg&h=49872d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">葉翠翠<br />\n生 肖 屬 雞 ！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n碎碎05年港姐奪冠後，在大台月入一萬都唔知有無下，買入幾個北角寶馬山豪宅賽西湖單位，點知俾死敵袁彌明暗諷有人幫佢供樓！事過境遷，碎碎15年已經嫁人，仲托緊5個月雞b，名副其實，老母係雞，bb又係雞！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gd8h5r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gd8h5r.jpg&h=193b2c70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02Y81H3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02Y81H3.jpg&h=430f7e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">李施嬅<br />\n生 肖 屬 雞 ！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n李施嬅早年家道中落，被食女專家鄧賤人玩到謝後，分手收場。有指男方常在朋友面前數臭李施嬅係正宗港女，只係識用男友錢。分手後，35歲嘅施嬅專mark有錢仔，希望能夠早日嫁入豪門。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/020024_5f9b823036ebc7b605711319ba5535cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F020024_5f9b823036ebc7b605711319ba5535cb.jpg&h=b955a2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">李詩韻<br />\n生 肖 屬 雞 ！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n李詩韻早年家道中落，被食女專家鄧賤人玩到謝後，分手收場。有指男方常在朋友面前數臭李詩韻係正宗港女，只係識用男友錢。分手後，35歲嘅詩韻專mark有錢仔，希望山雞變鳳凰，早日嫁入豪門。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/020055_d646c1769212e5fe02bd3eefa8ede700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F020055_d646c1769212e5fe02bd3eefa8ede700.jpg&h=2f137653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃翠如<br />\n生 肖 屬 雞 ！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n2014年5月，東方新地以「蕭家插旗 瞓何傲芝舊床 黃翠如 蕭正楠纏綿60小時」為題，令一向賣純情的翠如狐性盡現，可能是狐術，令翠如看起來像隻雞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/020330_b507688e8d8078ce2e7eb4a8562a0641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F020330_b507688e8d8078ce2e7eb4a8562a0641.jpg&h=9f736ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9cWodi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9cWodi1.jpg&h=0963a8d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">奉 勸 以 上 咁 多 位<br />\n雞 年 犯 太 歲 <br />\n小 心 為 上</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Sorry for the long post<br />\nHere is a box of chicken！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/020530_e661f81e9a716387c2b713310e4c7d35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F020530_e661f81e9a716387c2b713310e4c7d35.jpg&h=b34f971c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b6c6040552991d0cc35ff5dca7ac3530da3d677","tid":93871,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:16:08.000Z","msg":"李施嬅同李詩韻都係35歲咩 唔係詩韻大2年咩"},{"pid":"a39a7717a66107b1595a4466faba01d3c2ed2a68","tid":93871,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>李施嬅同李詩韻都係35歲咩 唔係詩韻大2年咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://entretenimento.r7.com/blogs/alvaro-leme/files/2015/08/&Eacute;-tudo-culpa-do-Aecio.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fentretenimento.r